ipmon (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium
  * Added error handling for socket initialization
  * Improved netlink message parsing
  * Enhanced IPv6 network support
  * Fixed memory leaks in address handling
  * Added hostname resolution
  * Improved configuration file handling
  * Better systemd integration
  * Added support for interface network masks
  * Enhanced proxy reload mechanism
  * Added robust error logging

ipmon (0.0.1) unstable; urgency=medium
  * Initial release
  * Network interface monitoring with IPv4/IPv6 support
  * Real-time NFTables rule updates
  * Proxy configuration management
  * Unix socket IPC support
  * Systemd service integration
  * Configurable update delay with debouncing
  * Thread-safe operation
  * Comprehensive logging